Developer Terms of Use
des: Volunteer aviation enthusiasts from around the world relay their local air traffic control frequencies to the Internet. A sampling of these broadcasts from August 10th, 2021 was captured and downloaded, and then stripped of long silences. Segments range from 1-30 minutes and are played on a continuous randomized shuffle.
